        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You have taken it upon yourself to learn the ways of combat to aid with your tasks, perhaps in a role as a corrector. You are trained with the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Composite Shortbow], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Glaive], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Longspear], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Longsword], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Shortbow], and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Spear]. You also gain access to all uncommon conrasu weapons(@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Buugeng]). For the purpose of determining your proficiency, martial conrasu weapons are simple weapons and advanced conrasu weapons are martial weapons.</p>"
